testsuite.name: org.apache.openwhisk.core.controller.test.KindRestrictorTests

testcase.name: Kind Restrictor should grant subject access to all kinds when no limits exist and no white list is defined
Kind Restrictor should grant subject access to any kinds if limit is the empty set
Kind Restrictor should grant subject access to any kinds if white list is the empty set
Kind Restrictor should grant subject access only to subject-limited kinds
Kind Restrictor should grant subject access to white listed kinds when no limits exist
Kind Restrictor should grant subject access both explicitly limited kinds and default whitelisted kinds
